 but we have good reasons to believe they do exist.
 However there are good reasons to believe that PRGs do exist.
 Many candidates are known whose security can be reduced to seemingly hard problems.
 Furthermore,
 it was shown that PRGs can be constructed based on any 
\emph on
One-way function
