\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Pr_{k}\left[\mathcal{A}\left(\vec{c}_{0}\right)=1\right]=1\neq0=\Pr_{k}\left[\mathcal{A}\left(\vec{c}_{1}\right)=1\right]
\]

\end_inset

and thus for any 
\begin_inset Formula $\varepsilon\in\left[0,1\right]$
